OL,3,CDouble child-killer Colin Pitchfork to
OL,4,Cface new parole hearing this week
OL,6,FDouble child-killer Colin Pitchfork is
OL,7,Fto face a new parole hearing this
OL,8,Fweek. Pitchfork raped and strangled 15-
OL,9,Fyear-olds Lynda Mann and Dawn Ashworth
OL,10,Fin Enderby and Narborough in
OL,11,FLeicestershire in the 1980s.
OL,13,FIn 1988, he was sentenced to life
OL,14,Fbehind bars with a minimum term of 28
OL,15,Fyears, which has now passed. He
OL,16,Fconvinced the Parole Board to release
OL,17,Fhim in 2021, but he was soon back
OL,18,Fbehind bars after breaching his
OL,19,Frelease conditions.
