OL,3,CDouble child-killer Colin Pitchfork to
OL,4,Cface new parole hearing this week
OL,6,FPitchfork made a new attempt to regain
OL,7,Fhis freedom in 2023, but failed with
OL,8,Fthe board deciding to keep him
OL,9,Fincarcerated.
OL,11,FThis latest bid for release has been
OL,12,Fmired in delays. A parole hearing was
OL,13,Fdue to take place in late 2024, but
OL,14,Fwas postponed when Pitchfork
OL,15,Funsuccessfully pursued a judicial
OL,16,Freview related to claims that he
OL,17,F"sexually assaulted" another prisoner.
