OL,3,CDouble child-killer Colin Pitchfork to
OL,4,Cface new parole hearing this week
OL,6,FMP for South Leicestershire Alberto
OL,7,FCosta has long campaigned to keep
OL,8,FPitchfork behind bars. He said: "I
OL,9,Funderstand the deep frustration many
OL,10,Ffeel at these continued twists and
OL,11,Fturns.
OL,13,F"My hope, however, is that the Parole
OL,14,FBoard recognises the risks of release
OL,15,Fare too great, and that we can finally
OL,16,Fdraw a line under this matter for the
OL,17,Ftime being.
