OL,3,CDouble child-killer Colin Pitchfork to
OL,4,Cface new parole hearing this week
OL,6,F"I am also campaigning to reform the
OL,7,Frules that have allowed this single
OL,8,Fparole bid to drag on for years. The
OL,9,FReconsideration Mechanism was never
OL,10,Fintended to permit endless, cost-free
OL,11,Fchallenges by a prisoner because they
OL,12,Fdislike the decision reached. Whilst I
OL,13,Fagree with the spirit of the rules,
OL,14,Fvictims and the public are denied
OL,15,Fclosure"
